24. Qe3 {.}) 22. Rxa1 {QUESTION: What should Black play here? --- ANSWER:} f6
$1 {Of course! Despite the absence of the queens and the fact that she has
given up the a-file, Black continues to play actively. This thematic pawn
break in French structures can be useful even in the endgame.} 23. Ng4 $6 (23.
